label: Date
desc: Date of observation of the row's data in YYYY-MM-DD format

label: Country
desc: Country in which the the row's data was observed

label: Cumulative Cases
desc: Cumulative number of confirmed cases as of the row's date, for the row's country

label: Daily Cases
desc: Daily new number of confirmed cases on the row's date, for the row's country

label: Active Cases
desc: Number of active cases (i.e., confirmed cases that still didn't recover nor die) on the row's date, for the row's country

label: Cumulative Deaths
desc: Cumulative number of confirmed deaths as of the row's date, for the row's country

label: Daily Deaths
desc: Daily new number of confirmed deaths on the row's date, for the row's country

label: Total Cases
desc: Total number of confirmed cases in the observed country

label: Total Deaths
desc: Total number of confirmed deaths in the observed country

label: Total Recoveries
desc: Total number of confirmed recoveries in the observed country

label: Active Cases
desc: Number of active cases in the observed country

label: Serious Cases
desc: Estimated number of cases in serious or critical conditions in the observed country

label: Cases per M
desc: Number of total cases per 1 million population in the observed country

label: Deaths per M
desc: Number of total deaths per 1 million population in the observed country

label: Total Tests
desc: Number of total tests done in the observed country

label: Tests per M
desc: Number of total test done per 1 million population in the observed country

label: Population
desc: Population count in the observed country
